You may not seem to grasp this concept, but many of the people in the guilds still tackling Vox and Naggy need several days advanced notice, if not longer, in order to go.  They don't want to do this with a group of people they've never met.  Many of these people have very long-standing friends in the guilds they are in and want to accomplish these goals together.  By refusing these very simple considerate actions, you're removing these people's chance.<br>
